title: Wise Program Uninstaller 1.96 Portable
description:
Wise Program Uninstaller 1.96 Portable


Download, unzip and use.  It is portable and free too.  Enjoy.  I just love portables!




Uninstall Programs And Remove Leftovers


Wise Program Uninstaller enables you to completely uninstall any program without leaving leftover files or registry entries behind.
When you choose to uninstall an application, Wise Uninstaller first launches the standard Uninstaller (that came with the application) and then performs a quick scan to searche for leftover file, folders or registry entries. If any are found, it presents you with a list and allows you to delete them.
The program can also try to repair broken uninstall entries, force removal of stubborn applications and remove invalid uninstall entries.
